{"word":"G66 - ἄγριος - ágrios - ag'-ree-os - Wild","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄγριος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ágrios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ag'-ree-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wild</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"காட்டு (காடு) அமளியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"living or growing in the fields or the woods, fierce, untamed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G68 - ἀγρός - agrós - ag-ros'/68\">G68</a>; <i>wild</i> (as pertaining to the <i>country</i>), literally (<i>natural</i>) or figuratively (<i>fierce</i>): - wild, raging.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}